fields.name: Category
fields.description: Name of a Diagnostic Log category for a resource type this setting is applied to. To obtain the list of Diagnostic Log categories for a resource, first perform a GET diagnostic settings operation.

fields.name: CategoryGroup
fields.description: Name of a Diagnostic Log category group for a resource type this setting is applied to. To obtain the list of Diagnostic Log categories for a resource, first perform a GET diagnostic settings operation.

fields.name: Enabled
fields.description: a value indicating whether this log is enabled.

fields.name: RetentionPolicy
fields.description: the retention policy for this log.
